  "detailed_description": "You can stack blocks to make your own building. There are several obstructions. You should overcome earthquake, cat, bomb. Your goal is to maintain the building height after disaster.<br />\r\nThere are 6 shapes and 3 material of block. weight, restitution coefficient, friction are different by material.<br />\r\nThere are total 48 levels. Also, You can make your own map. There are 3 slots to save your own map.<br />\r\nThis game is 2d graphic, blocks move by physics law.",
